==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slugworm
<hw>Slug"worm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any caterpillar which has the general appearance of a slug, as do
those of certain moths belonging to <gen>Limacodes</gen> and allied
genera, and those of certain sawflies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sluice</ent>⟦br⟧
